lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.ArmorUpgr.name: STANDARD ARMOR
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.ArmorUpgr.description: Standard BattleMech armor that provides 32 points of protection per ton.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.ArmorUpgr.name: FERRO FIBROUS ARMOR
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.ArmorUpgr.description: 12% more protection per ton, occupies 14 critical slots but weighs less.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.Structure.name: STANDARD STRUCTURE
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.Structure.description: The internal “bones” of a 'Mech, uses standard materials and weighs 10% of the 'Mech’s maximum tonnage.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.Structure.name: ENDO-STEEL STRUCTURE
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.Structure.description: Made from lighter endo-steel and weighing 5% of the 'Mech’s maximum tonnage but occupies 14 critical slots.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.HeatSinkU.name: STANDARD HEAT SINK
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.HeatSinkU.description: A standard heat sink that dissipates heat generated by the 'Mech's engine, weapon systems and the environment's ambient temperature.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.HeatSinkU.name: DOUBLE HEAT SINK
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.HeatSinkU.description: 40% more efficient than a Standard Heat Sink but weighing the same; requires triple the amount of space.

lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.GuidanceU.name: ARTEMIS
lisong__mechlab.model.upgrades.GuidanceU.description: A targeting system that increases LRM and SRM accuracy. Each ARTEMIS-enabled weapon takes one more slot. Must be equipped with ARTEMIS equipped ammunition which is twice as expensive.
